snippet.textDisplay:
I am so captivated or rather say mesmerised by this track… the strength of lyrics and the powerhouse of vocals complementing it… this song is like nostalgic feel of music made in 90’s… a track which is a complete package of lyrics, vocals, beats,  visuals… but enhanced with a modern touch while holding on to the classic one. Which makes this track like a fine wine… the older the better 

Star Shah’s crosses your heart like an arrow, sharp, honest, brutal reality hitting deep, like any honest person can relate to the betrayal and grievance, but Zeeshan Ali’s part is like fresh flowing spring water in a scorching hot sun, like a ray of hope, lyrics really touch your heart leaving a soothing effect on your soul. They created a masterpiece. Just look at reactions even ppl who don’t understand the language  are touched by it. 

If there is a ritual of bowing down to music… this track makes me do that 🙌 welldone everyone involved… I will keep coming back to this track for the rest of my life ❤
